description: Try our easy to follow Spicy Chicken Noodles recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Spicy Chicken Noodles Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat remaining oil in frying pan. Add vegetables and stir-fry for 5 minutes or until just tender. Add noodles and soy. Return chicken to pan and toss to combine. Cook for 2 minutes or until heated through. Serve.
